posts.description: What a day...start to finish issues including my blog being down, etc. I do have a gorgeous new post on the blog today with dinnerware that I'd love for you to see! Thanks everyone for your amazing support here on Instagram and the blog. You make these stinky days shine! 😘

I often arrange the prettiest of flowers into the plainest of containers, but tomorrow on the blog I'm sharing something very special! If you aren't subscribed I have a free seasonal decorating book to download when you do. See you in the morning friends...sweet dreams!  #flowers #ranunculus #seasonal #design #entertaining #centerpieces #pool #miamistyle

A hidden garden lost and found revealed on the blog today! Swipe left to see some of my finds that will be part of my new found spot and I scored them all at @beallsoutlet #ad at up to 70% off at the Garden Event going on through May 4th! #garden #event #shopping #design #decorating #topiary #mossball #greenery #eatcraftdiy

We were able to salvage these 14 year old cabinets, diy the tile and some other projects and heading back next weekend for more work and getting closer to that light at the of the tunnel. Or reno...as in this case. Cheers 🥂 and see my previous post and link in profile for today's blog post on a totally different kitchen! #kitchen #diy #renovation #whitekitchen #beachhouse #coastaldecor
A little story about this kitchen on the blog today and why it's important to infuse your own style and not follow all trends. Hope you pop over for the anecdote too!

Off the radar with our beach home kitchen remodeling, and wanted to share this beauty from my friend Jayme from @fridleyhomes_design who designs the most beautiful homes! Our kitchen is tiny in comparison, but it's so much fun scouring her feed for inspiration! Happy Saturday friends.

My #onetofollow this evening is my friend Matthew Mead, who is an amazing creative soul, a fabulously talented stylist, photographer, and just an all around great and humble hard working guy. He's always been a huge inspiration and supporter to so many and I'm giving his newest publication a shout out tonight for your support to keep magazines in print! You'll find this one at @barnesandnoble and it's full of eye candy! @matthewmeadstyle #magazines #publishing #stylist #photographer

I'm sharing a blogging journey today & am so excited to have been chosen not only to teach photography again, but I'll be doing double duty as a mentor at The Haven Conference this year! Are you going? And today we just arrived at our beach home and I'll be sharing our kitchen renovation #diy on Stories here! Happy Friday friends...I'm declaring it the weekend 😀 #havenconf  #lifestyleblogger #lifeisgood #photographer #beachhouse

We recently had the exterior of our home painted and there was just something about the front doors that didn’t seem in synch with the updates that we’ve been making to our outside spaces. Our goal was a welcoming and updated look that went well with the tropical climate we call home. Our front doors have been painted black for a long time and I gathered inspiration by the colors of the sea, so I headed to Lowe’s with some ideas and swatches and they were able to match what I had in mind! We love the updated look and the ease and quality of the paint that we purchased too! “Love your paint, it’s guaranteed” #AD #PaintWithLowes http://low.es/2nvQ30D

So excited for some announcements coming to the blog tomorrow that just might involve photography and the fact that I've been around the block a few dozen times. Or so it seems! 😝 Link to the blog is in my profile and this image is from a previous post if you'd like to poke around today. Wishing you a great day!
